<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="介護福祉士国家試験 頻出語リスト">
    <meta name="keywords" content="介護福祉士国家試験, 頻出語, リスト">
    <title>{{ title }}</title>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@700&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;500;700&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="word_book_print.css">
</head>
<body>
    <main class="page" aria-label="単語リスト">
        <header class="list-header">
            <h1 class="list-caption">{{ title }}</h1>
            <div class="freq-legend" role="note" aria-label="頻度の目安">
                <p>★★★「最頻出語：本試験で特によく出る最重要語」</p>
                <p>★★「頻出語：出題頻度が高く優先して覚えたい語」</p>
                <p>★「基礎・準頻出語：理解しておきたい土台の語」</p>
            </div>
        </header>

        {% for e in entries %}
        <section class="word-group" id="w-{{ e.index }}">
            <div class="word-row-main">
                <div class="word-main-flex" role="row">
                    <label class="flex-cell col-check">
                        <input type="checkbox" class="word-check" name="word-{{ e.index }}" value="{{ e.index }}"
                            aria-label="{{ e.index }} {{ e.word }} をマーク">
                    </label>
                    <div class="flex-cell col-no" aria-hidden="true"></div>
                    <div class="flex-cell col-word">
                        <div class="table-word">{{ e.word_ruby | safe }}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-cell col-meaning">
                        <span class="col-meaning-inner">{{ e.meaning_html | safe }}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-cell col-en">
                        <span class="col-en-pos" aria-hidden="true">[{{ e.pos }}]</span>
                        <span class="col-en-text">{{ e.english }}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="word-row-example">
                <div class="example-block">
                    {{ e.example_html | safe }}<span class="card-source">[{{ e.source }}]</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        {% endfor %}
    </main>
</body>
</html>
